{"uid":"4c713c76321cf9f4","name":"test_concurrent_mixed_bodies_are_serialized_with_conflict","fullName":"tests.api.test_api_concurrency.TestPostExpenseConcurrency#test_concurrent_mixed_bodies_are_serialized_with_conflict","historyId":"b0a6ceeb485f0f04b86e36a278f82817","time":{"start":1781768809769,"stop":1781768809891,"duration":122},"description":"Concurrent variant of the conflict path: N racers share a\n``client_expense_id`` but differ on ``amount``.\n\nThe atomic ON CONFLICT compare inside ``insert_expense`` must\nstill pick exactly one winner (the first writer to commit),\nand every other racer must land in the compare branch and\nsurface a **409 Conflict** — not a 500 ``OperationalError``\nleak, and not a silent 200 duplicate that would hide an actual\npayload disagreement from the PWA.\n\nThis complements\n``test_concurrent_replays_are_serialized_without_transaction_errors``:\nthat one covers the idempotent-replay branch (identical\nbodies -> 200 duplicate for the losers), this one covers the\nconflicting-body branch (different bodies -> 409 for the\nlosers). Together they exercise both recovery exits from the\n``sqlite3.IntegrityError`` / ``sqlite3.OperationalError``\ncompare path.\n","descriptionHtml":"<p>Concurrent variant of the conflict path: N racers share a<br />\n<code>client_expense_id</code> but differ on <code>amount</code>.</p>\n<p>The atomic ON CONFLICT compare inside <code>insert_expense</code> must<br />\nstill pick exactly one winner (the first writer to commit),<br />\nand every other racer must land in the compare branch and<br />\nsurface a <strong>409 Conflict</strong> — not a 500 <code>OperationalError</code><br />\nleak, and not a silent 200 duplicate that would hide an actual<br />\npayload disagreement from the PWA.</p>\n<p>This complements<br />\n<code>test_concurrent_replays_are_serialized_without_transaction_errors</code>:<br />\nthat one covers the idempotent-replay branch (identical<br />\nbodies -&gt; 200 duplicate for the losers), this one covers the<br />\nconflicting-body branch (different bodies -&gt; 409 for the<br />\nlosers). Together they exercise both recovery exits from the<br />\n<code>sqlite3.IntegrityError</code> / <code>sqlite3.OperationalError</code><br />\ncompare path.</p>\n","status":"passed","flaky":false,"newFailed":false,"newBroken":false,"newPassed":false,"retriesCount":0,"retriesStatusChange":false,"beforeStages":[{"name":"_stub_socket_getfqdn","time":{"start":1781768796393,"stop":1781768796393,"duration":0},"status":"passed","steps":[],"attachments":[],"parameters":[],"hasContent":false,"stepsCount":0,"shouldDisplayMessage":false,"attachmentsCount":0,"attachmentStep":false},{"name":"tmp_path_factory","time":{"start":1781768796394,"stop":1781768796394,"duration":0},"status":"passed","steps":[],"attachments":[],"parameters":[],"hasContent":false,"stepsCount":0,"shouldDisplayMessage":false,"attachmentsCount":0,"attachmentStep":false},{"name":"blank_db","time":{"start":1781768796394,"stop":1781768796625,"duration":231},"status":"passed","steps":[],"attachments":[],"parameters":[],"hasContent":false,"stepsCount":0,"shouldDisplayMessage":false,"attachmentsCount":0,"attachmentStep":false},{"name":"monkeypatch","time":{"start":1781768809763,"stop":1781768809763,"duration":0},"status":"passed","steps":[],"attachments":[],"parameters":[],"hasContent":false,"stepsCount":0,"shouldDisplayMessage":false,"attachmentsCount":0,"attachmentStep":false},{"name":"_disable_llm_seed","time":{"start":1781768809764,"stop":1781768809764,"duration":0},"status":"passed","steps":[],"attachments":[],"parameters":[],"hasContent":false,"stepsCount":0,"shouldDisplayMessage":false,"attachmentsCount":0,"attachmentStep":false},{"name":"_disable_sheet_mapping_preload","time":{"start":1781768809764,"stop":1781768809764,"duration":0},"status":"passed","steps":[],"attachments":[],"parameters":[],"hasContent":false,"stepsCount":0,"shouldDisplayMessage":false,"attachmentsCount":0,"attachmentStep":false},{"na